\v 4 \w Now|strong="G1161"\w* \w to|strong="G2596"\w* \w him|strong="G3588"\w* \w who|strong="G3588"\w* \w works|strong="G2038"\w*, \w the|strong="G1161"\w* \w pay|strong="G3408"\w* \w is|strong="G3588"\w* \w not|strong="G3756"\w* \w counted|strong="G3049"\w* \w as|strong="G1161"\w* \w a|strong="G3756"\w* \w gift|strong="G5485"\w* \w but|strong="G1161"\w* \w as|strong="G1161"\w* \w an|strong="G1161"\w* obligation.  
