\v 18 \w Contrary|strong="G3844"\w* \w to|strong="G1519"\w* \w hope|strong="G1680"\w*, \w Abraham|strong="G4100"\w* \w in|strong="G1519"\w* \w hope|strong="G1680"\w* \w believed|strong="G4100"\w*, \w so|strong="G3779"\w* \w as|strong="G1519"\w* \w to|strong="G1519"\w* \w become|strong="G1096"\w* \w a|strong="G1096"\w* \w father|strong="G3962"\w* \w of|strong="G3844"\w* \w many|strong="G4183"\w* ethnic \w nations|strong="G1484"\w*, \w according|strong="G2596"\w* \w to|strong="G1519"\w* \w what|strong="G3739"\w* \w had|strong="G1510"\w* \w been|strong="G1510"\w* \w spoken|strong="G3004"\w*: “\w So|strong="G3779"\w* \w shall|strong="G3739"\w* \w your|strong="G1909"\w* \w seed|strong="G4690"\w* \w be|strong="G1096"\w*.”\f + \fr 4:18 \ft See Genesis 15:5.\f*  
\v 19 \w And|strong="G2532"\w* \w not|strong="G3361"\w* \w being|strong="G5225"\w* weak \w in|strong="G2532"\w* \w faith|strong="G4102"\w*, \w he|strong="G2532"\w* \w did|strong="G2532"\w* \w not|strong="G3361"\w*\f + \fr 4:19 \ft Perhaps 3% of the Greek manuscripts (of objectively inferior quality) omit “not”, to be followed by NIV, NASB, TEV, LB, etc.—an inferior proceeding.\f* \w consider|strong="G2657"\w* \w his|strong="G1438"\w* \w own|strong="G1438"\w* \w body|strong="G4983"\w*, already \w dead|strong="G3499"\w*\f + \fr 4:19 \ft Paul declares that Abraham had become impotent before begetting Isaac. That means that he had started slowing down long before, and no one would be more aware of that than Sarah. That may explain why she offered Hagar—she was aware of the Promise and Abraham needed a descendant.\f* (\w being|strong="G5225"\w* \w about|strong="G4225"\w* \w a|strong="G2532"\w* \w hundred|strong="G1541"\w* \w years|strong="G1541"\w* \w old|strong="G1541"\w*), \w or|strong="G2532"\w* \w the|strong="G2532"\w* \w deadness|strong="G3500"\w* \w of|strong="G2532"\w* \w Sarah|strong="G4564"\w*'s \w womb|strong="G3388"\w*.  
\v 20 \w He|strong="G1161"\w* \w did|strong="G2316"\w* \w not|strong="G3756"\w* \w waver|strong="G1252"\w* \w at|strong="G1519"\w* \w God|strong="G2316"\w*'s \w promise|strong="G1860"\w* \w in|strong="G1519"\w* unbelief; \w rather|strong="G3756"\w*, \w he|strong="G1161"\w* \w was|strong="G3588"\w* \w strengthened|strong="G1743"\w* \w by|strong="G1519"\w* \w the|strong="G1519"\w* \w faith|strong="G4102"\w*, \w giving|strong="G1325"\w* \w glory|strong="G1391"\w* \w to|strong="G1519"\w* \w God|strong="G2316"\w*,  
