\s1 Newness of life  
\m
\v 1 \w So|strong="G2443"\w* \w what|strong="G5101"\w* \w shall|strong="G5101"\w* \w we|strong="G2443"\w* \w say|strong="G3004"\w*? \w Shall|strong="G5101"\w* \w we|strong="G2443"\w* \w continue|strong="G1961"\w* \w in|strong="G1961"\w* \w the|strong="G3588"\w* sin \w so|strong="G2443"\w* \w that|strong="G2443"\w* \w the|strong="G3588"\w* \w grace|strong="G5485"\w* \w may|strong="G2443"\w* \w abound|strong="G4121"\w*?  
