\s2 Law and sin  
\p
\v 7 \w So|strong="G3767"\w* \w what|strong="G5101"\w* \w shall|strong="G5101"\w* \w we|strong="G1063"\w* \w say|strong="G3004"\w* \w then|strong="G3767"\w*? \w Is|strong="G3588"\w* \w the|strong="G1223"\w* \w law|strong="G3551"\w* sin? \w Of|strong="G1223"\w* course \w not|strong="G3756"\w*! \w Indeed|strong="G1063"\w*, \w I|strong="G1063"\w* \w would|strong="G1096"\w* \w not|strong="G3756"\w* \w have|strong="G1096"\w* \w come|strong="G1096"\w* \w to|strong="G3004"\w* \w know|strong="G1492"\w* \w the|strong="G1223"\w* sin\f + \fr 7:7 \ft If not a synonym for the fallen nature, or ‘the flesh’, ‘the sin’ appears to be closely related to it. ‘The flesh’ is Satan's ally inside us while ‘the world’ is his ally outside us. So without the Holy Spirit a person is in a bad way.\f* \w except|strong="G1487"\w* \w through|strong="G1223"\w* \w the|strong="G1223"\w* \w law|strong="G3551"\w*: \w I|strong="G1063"\w* \w would|strong="G1096"\w* \w not|strong="G3756"\w* \w have|strong="G1096"\w* \w recognized|strong="G1097"\w* covetousness \w if|strong="G1487"\w* \w the|strong="G1223"\w* \w law|strong="G3551"\w* \w had|strong="G3588"\w* \w not|strong="G3756"\w* \w said|strong="G3004"\w*, “\w You|strong="G1487"\w* \w must|strong="G2046"\w* \w not|strong="G3756"\w* \w covet|strong="G1937"\w*.”  
\v 8 \w But|strong="G1161"\w* \w the|strong="G1722"\w* sin, grasping \w an|strong="G1722"\w* opportunity \w through|strong="G1223"\w* \w the|strong="G1722"\w* \w commandment|strong="G1785"\w*, \w produced|strong="G2716"\w* \w in|strong="G1722"\w* \w me|strong="G1473"\w* \w all|strong="G3956"\w* \w kinds|strong="G3956"\w* \w of|strong="G1223"\w* \w coveting|strong="G1939"\w*.\f + \fr 7:8 \ft Anyone who has children has seen this principle at work (also if he can still remember how it was when he was a child). Once upon a time there was a doctrine that said that the children of Christians are born without a sin nature—I have always thought that the only people who could believe that would be people with no children!\f*  
\p \w Now|strong="G1161"\w* \w without|strong="G5565"\w* \w the|strong="G1722"\w* \w law|strong="G3551"\w* sin \w is|strong="G3588"\w* \w dead|strong="G3498"\w*.  
\v 9 \w Once|strong="G4218"\w* \w upon|strong="G3588"\w* \w a|strong="G2064"\w* \w time|strong="G4218"\w*, \w without|strong="G5565"\w* \w law|strong="G3551"\w*, \w I|strong="G1473"\w* \w was|strong="G3588"\w* actually ‘\w alive|strong="G2198"\w*’; \w but|strong="G1161"\w* \w when|strong="G1161"\w* \w the|strong="G1161"\w* \w commandment|strong="G1785"\w* \w came|strong="G2064"\w*, \w the|strong="G1161"\w* sin \w came|strong="G2064"\w* \w to|strong="G2064"\w* \w life|strong="G2198"\w* \w and|strong="G1161"\w* \w I|strong="G1473"\w* \w died|strong="G3588"\w*.  
\v 10 \w Yes|strong="G1161"\w*, \w the|strong="G2532"\w* \w commandment|strong="G1785"\w* \w that|strong="G3588"\w* \w was|strong="G3588"\w* \w to|strong="G1519"\w* \w bring|strong="G2532"\w* \w me|strong="G1473"\w* \w life|strong="G2222"\w* turned \w out|strong="G2532"\w* \w to|strong="G1519"\w* \w bring|strong="G2532"\w* \w death|strong="G2288"\w*.  
\v 11 \w Because|strong="G1223"\w* \w the|strong="G2532"\w* sin, grasping \w an|strong="G2532"\w* opportunity \w through|strong="G1223"\w* \w the|strong="G2532"\w* \w commandment|strong="G1785"\w*, completely \w deceived|strong="G1818"\w* \w me|strong="G1473"\w*, \w and|strong="G2532"\w* used \w it|strong="G2532"\w* \w to|strong="G2532"\w* ‘kill’ \w me|strong="G1473"\w*.  
