\q2 \w Or|strong="G2228"\w* \w who|strong="G5101"\w* \w has|strong="G2962"\w* \w been|strong="G1096"\w* \w His|strong="G2228"\w* \w counselor|strong="G4825"\w*?”\f + \fr 11:34 \ft See Isaiah 40:13 and Jeremiah 23:18.\f*   
\q1
\v 35 \w Or|strong="G2228"\w* “\w Who|strong="G5101"\w* \w has|strong="G5101"\w* ever \w given|strong="G4272"\w* \w to|strong="G2532"\w* \w Him|strong="G2532"\w* \w and|strong="G2532"\w* \w has|strong="G5101"\w* \w to|strong="G2532"\w* \w be|strong="G2532"\w* repaid?”\f + \fr 11:35 \ft See Job 41:11.\f*   
\q1
\v 36 \w Because|strong="G3754"\w* \w from|strong="G1537"\w* \w Him|strong="G3588"\w* \w and|strong="G2532"\w* \w through|strong="G1223"\w* \w Him|strong="G3588"\w* \w and|strong="G2532"\w* \w to|strong="G1519"\w* \w Him|strong="G3588"\w*  
\q2 \w are|strong="G3588"\w* \w all|strong="G3956"\w* \w things|strong="G3956"\w*.\f + \fr 11:36 \ft Everything said and done, God is the Owner of the universe.\f*  
\q1 \w To|strong="G1519"\w* \w Him|strong="G3588"\w* \w be|strong="G2532"\w* \w the|strong="G2532"\w* \w glory|strong="G1391"\w* \w forever|strong="G1519"\w*! Amen.   
\c 12  
\ms1 The will of God  
\m
\v 1 \w Now|strong="G3767"\w* \w then|strong="G3767"\w*, brothers, \w I|strong="G1223"\w* \w exhort|strong="G3870"\w* \w you|strong="G5210"\w*, \w in|strong="G2316"\w* \w view|strong="G1223"\w* \w of|strong="G1223"\w* \w God|strong="G2316"\w*'s compassions, \w to|strong="G2316"\w* \w present|strong="G3936"\w* \w your|strong="G1223"\w* \w bodies|strong="G4983"\w* \w as|strong="G2316"\w* \w a|strong="G1223"\w* \w living|strong="G2198"\w* \w sacrifice|strong="G2378"\w*,\f + \fr 12:1 \ft Any animal in the Old Testament had to die in order to become a sacrifice, so what does Paul mean by a ‘living’ one? In 1 Corinthians 15:31 he said that he died every day. Paul could not have been referring to actual physical death, obviously, since Hebrews 9:27 affirms that it is appointed to men to die only once (no reincarnation). He may well have faced possible death often enough, but I suppose he is referring to dying to himself. I suppose this is also the meaning of our Lord's words in Luke 9:23-24—“If anyone desires to come after me, let him deny himself, and take up his cross daily, and follow me. For whoever desires to save his life will lose it, but whoever loses his life for my sake will save it.” In that day a cross was an instrument of death. We must die to our own will in order to embrace God's. To present the body is presumably a metonym for presenting one's whole self.\f* holy, satisfying \w to|strong="G2316"\w* \w God|strong="G2316"\w*—\w your|strong="G1223"\w* intelligent duty.  
\v 2 Yes, \w stop|strong="G3361"\w* conforming \w to|strong="G1519"\w* \w the|strong="G2532"\w* pattern \w of|strong="G2532"\w* \w this|strong="G3778"\w* world; rather, \w be|strong="G2532"\w* \w transformed|strong="G3339"\w* \w by|strong="G2532"\w* \w the|strong="G2532"\w* renewing \w of|strong="G2532"\w* \w your|strong="G2532"\w* \w mind|strong="G3563"\w* \w so|strong="G2532"\w* \w as|strong="G1519"\w* \w to|strong="G1519"\w* \w be|strong="G2532"\w* able \w to|strong="G1519"\w* experience \w the|strong="G2532"\w* \w good|strong="G5101"\w* \w and|strong="G2532"\w* satisfying \w and|strong="G2532"\w* \w perfect|strong="G5046"\w* \w will|strong="G2307"\w* \w of|strong="G2532"\w* \w God|strong="G2316"\w*.\f + \fr 12:2 \ft ‘The pattern of this world’ belongs to Satan, so it must be rejected in order to do God's will. Many ‘Christians’ appear to be afraid of God's will, as well they might, unless they meet the conditions—only then is it ‘good’, ‘satisfying’ and ‘perfect’.\f*   
\s1 Be sensible  
\p
\v 3 Based \w on|strong="G1722"\w* \w the|strong="G1722"\w* \w grace|strong="G5485"\w* \w given|strong="G1325"\w* \w to|strong="G1519"\w* \w me|strong="G1325"\w*, \w I|strong="G1473"\w* \w say|strong="G3004"\w* \w to|strong="G1519"\w* \w everyone|strong="G3956"\w* \w among|strong="G1722"\w* \w you|strong="G5210"\w* \w not|strong="G3361"\w* \w to|strong="G1519"\w* \w set|strong="G5426"\w* \w your|strong="G1223"\w* sights higher \w than|strong="G3844"\w* \w you|strong="G5210"\w* \w should|strong="G1163"\w*, \w but|strong="G3361"\w* \w set|strong="G5426"\w* \w them|strong="G3588"\w* sensibly, \w as|strong="G5613"\w* \w God|strong="G2316"\w* \w has|strong="G2316"\w* \w apportioned|strong="G3307"\w* \w a|strong="G5613"\w* \w measure|strong="G3358"\w* \w of|strong="G1223"\w* \w faith|strong="G4102"\w* \w to|strong="G1519"\w* \w each|strong="G1538"\w*.\f + \fr 12:3 \ft We need to understand what God wants us to be and do, and set our sights on that. Any attitude of competition, wanting to be bigger and better than others, will produce bad results.\f*  
\v 4 \w Because|strong="G1063"\w* \w just|strong="G2509"\w* \w as|strong="G1722"\w* \w in|strong="G1722"\w* \w one|strong="G1520"\w* \w body|strong="G4983"\w* \w we|strong="G1063"\w* \w have|strong="G2192"\w* \w many|strong="G4183"\w* \w parts|strong="G3196"\w*, \w but|strong="G1161"\w* \w all|strong="G3956"\w* \w the|strong="G1722"\w* \w parts|strong="G3196"\w* \w do|strong="G2192"\w* \w not|strong="G3756"\w* \w have|strong="G2192"\w* \w the|strong="G1722"\w* same \w function|strong="G4234"\w*,  
\v 5 \w so|strong="G3779"\w* \w we|strong="G1161"\w*, \w who|strong="G3588"\w* \w are|strong="G1510"\w* \w many|strong="G4183"\w*, \w are|strong="G1510"\w* \w one|strong="G1520"\w* \w body|strong="G4983"\w* \w in|strong="G1722"\w* \w Christ|strong="G5547"\w* \w and|strong="G1161"\w* \w individually|strong="G2596"\w* \w members|strong="G3196"\w* \w of|strong="G4983"\w* \w one|strong="G1520"\w* \w another|strong="G2596"\w*.  
\v 6 \w Since|strong="G2192"\w* \w we|strong="G2249"\w* \w have|strong="G2192"\w* \w different|strong="G1313"\w* \w spiritual|strong="G5486"\w* \w gifts|strong="G5486"\w* \w according|strong="G2596"\w* \w to|strong="G2596"\w* \w the|strong="G1161"\w* \w grace|strong="G5485"\w* \w that|strong="G3588"\w* \w was|strong="G3588"\w* \w given|strong="G1325"\w* \w us|strong="G1325"\w*, \it let us use them\it*: \w if|strong="G1535"\w* \w prophecy|strong="G4394"\w*, \w according|strong="G2596"\w* \w to|strong="G2596"\w* \w the|strong="G1161"\w* analogy \w of|strong="G5485"\w* \w the|strong="G1161"\w* \w Faith|strong="G4102"\w*;\f + \fr 12:6 \ft Any prophesying needs to be in accordance with Scripture.\f*  
\v 7 \w if|strong="G1535"\w* \w serving|strong="G1248"\w*, \w in|strong="G1722"\w* \w the|strong="G1722"\w* \w serving|strong="G1248"\w*; \w if|strong="G1535"\w* \w teaching|strong="G1321"\w*, \w in|strong="G1722"\w* \w the|strong="G1722"\w* \w teaching|strong="G1321"\w*;  
\v 8 \w if|strong="G1535"\w* \w exhorting|strong="G3870"\w*, \w in|strong="G1722"\w* \w the|strong="G1722"\w* \w exhortation|strong="G3874"\w*;\f + \fr 12:8 \ft One might feel that Paul is being repetitious, but we all know people who try to operate in someone else's area of gifting, and the results are not good. If an ear tries to be an eye, both hearing and sight suffer.\f* \w the|strong="G1722"\w* sharer, \w with|strong="G1722"\w* simplicity; \w the|strong="G1722"\w* leader, \w with|strong="G1722"\w* \w diligence|strong="G4710"\w*; \w the|strong="G1722"\w* mercy-shower, \w with|strong="G1722"\w* \w cheerfulness|strong="G2432"\w*.\f + \fr 12:8 \ft Nothing like cheerfulness when helping someone who is hurting.\f*   
\s1 Behave!  
\p
\v 9 Love \w is|strong="G3588"\w* \w to|strong="G3588"\w* \w be|strong="G3588"\w* genuine: abhorring \w the|strong="G3588"\w* \w malignant|strong="G4190"\w*; clinging \w to|strong="G3588"\w* \w the|strong="G3588"\w* \w good|strong="G3588"\w*;  
\v 10 showing family affection \w to|strong="G1519"\w* \w one|strong="G3588"\w* \w another|strong="G3588"\w* \w in|strong="G1519"\w* \w brotherly|strong="G5360"\w* \w love|strong="G5360"\w*; \w in|strong="G1519"\w* \w honor|strong="G5092"\w* \w preferring|strong="G4285"\w* \w one|strong="G3588"\w* \w another|strong="G3588"\w*;  
\v 11 \w not|strong="G3361"\w* \w lagging|strong="G3636"\w* \w in|strong="G3361"\w* \w diligence|strong="G4710"\w*; \w serving|strong="G1398"\w* \w the|strong="G3588"\w* \w Lord|strong="G2962"\w* \w with|strong="G2962"\w* \w an|strong="G3361"\w* enthusiastic \w spirit|strong="G4151"\w*;  
\v 12 \w rejoicing|strong="G5463"\w* \w in|strong="G3588"\w* \w the|strong="G3588"\w* \w hope|strong="G1680"\w*; enduring \w the|strong="G3588"\w* \w affliction|strong="G2347"\w*; \w continuing|strong="G4342"\w* steadfastly \w in|strong="G3588"\w* \w prayer|strong="G4335"\w*;  
\v 13 \w distributing|strong="G2841"\w* \w to|strong="G3588"\w* \w the|strong="G3588"\w* \w needs|strong="G5532"\w* \w of|strong="G5532"\w* \w the|strong="G3588"\w* saints; \w practicing|strong="G1377"\w* \w hospitality|strong="G5381"\w*.\f + \fr 12:13 \ft I take it that the whole paragraph is explaining just how love is to be genuine—very practical!\f*   
\p
\v 14 \w Bless|strong="G2127"\w* \w those|strong="G3588"\w* \w who|strong="G3588"\w* \w persecute|strong="G1377"\w* \w you|strong="G5210"\w*; \w bless|strong="G2127"\w* \w and|strong="G2532"\w* \w do|strong="G2532"\w* \w not|strong="G3361"\w* \w curse|strong="G2672"\w*.\f + \fr 12:14 \ft If a boss is mistreating you and you curse him, will he get better or worse? That said, however, I believe we must distinguish between things done against us personally and things done against the Kingdom. Something done against the Kingdom is an act of war, and needs to be repelled.\f*  
\v 15 \w Rejoice|strong="G5463"\w* \w with|strong="G3326"\w* those who \w rejoice|strong="G5463"\w* \w and|strong="G2799"\w* \w weep|strong="G2799"\w* \w with|strong="G3326"\w* those who \w weep|strong="G2799"\w*.  
\v 16 \w Regard|strong="G1519"\w* \w each|strong="G1438"\w* \w other|strong="G1438"\w* \w as|strong="G1519"\w* \w being|strong="G1096"\w* \w on|strong="G1519"\w* \w the|strong="G1519"\w* same level—\w do|strong="G1096"\w* \w not|strong="G3361"\w* distinguish \w the|strong="G1519"\w* upper classes, \w but|strong="G3361"\w* \w associate|strong="G4879"\w* \w with|strong="G3844"\w* \w the|strong="G1519"\w* lower classes; \w do|strong="G1096"\w* \w not|strong="G3361"\w* exalt \w yourself|strong="G1438"\w*.\f + \fr 12:16 \ft I take it that this text is dealing with social position, not personal abilities.\f*  
\v 17 \w Do|strong="G3367"\w* \w not|strong="G3367"\w* repay \w anyone|strong="G3367"\w* \w evil|strong="G2556"\w* \w for|strong="G2570"\w* \w evil|strong="G2556"\w*. \w Have|strong="G3956"\w* \w regard|strong="G4306"\w* \w for|strong="G2570"\w* \w things|strong="G3956"\w* \w that|strong="G3956"\w* \w everyone|strong="G3956"\w* considers \w to|strong="G3956"\w* \w be|strong="G3956"\w* \w good|strong="G2570"\w*.  
\v 18 \w If|strong="G1487"\w* \w possible|strong="G1415"\w*, \w what|strong="G3588"\w* \w depends|strong="G1537"\w* \w on|strong="G1537"\w* \w you|strong="G5210"\w*, \w live|strong="G1514"\w* \w at|strong="G1537"\w* \w peace|strong="G1514"\w* \w with|strong="G3326"\w* \w everyone|strong="G3956"\w*.   
\p
\v 19 Dear ones, \w do|strong="G3004"\w* \w not|strong="G3361"\w* \w avenge|strong="G1556"\w* \w yourselves|strong="G1438"\w*; rather \w give|strong="G1325"\w* \w place|strong="G5117"\w* \w to|strong="G3004"\w* \w the|strong="G3588"\w* \w wrath|strong="G3709"\w*;\f + \fr 12:19 \ft Wrath is normally expressed through physical violence, and perhaps in our day through legal action. These are the sort of reaction that an ‘enemy’ will expect, not acts of kindness, which may even make him feel ashamed of himself. In any case, we are not to descend to his level, but let God do any avenging.\f* \w for|strong="G1063"\w* \w it|strong="G1063"\w* \w is|strong="G3588"\w* \w written|strong="G1125"\w*: “\w Vengeance|strong="G1557"\w* \w is|strong="G3588"\w* \w up|strong="G1325"\w* \w to|strong="G3004"\w* \w me|strong="G1325"\w*; \w I|strong="G1473"\w* \w will|strong="G2962"\w* repay,”\f + \fr 12:19 \ft See Deuteronomy 32:35.\f* \w says|strong="G3004"\w* \w the|strong="G3588"\w* \w Lord|strong="G2962"\w*.  
\v 20 \w Therefore|strong="G1063"\w*, “\w If|strong="G1437"\w* \w your|strong="G1437"\w* \w enemy|strong="G2190"\w* \w is|strong="G3588"\w* \w hungry|strong="G3983"\w*, \w feed|strong="G5595"\w* \w him|strong="G3588"\w*; \w if|strong="G1437"\w* \w he|strong="G3778"\w* \w is|strong="G3588"\w* \w thirsty|strong="G1372"\w*, \w give|strong="G4160"\w* \w him|strong="G3588"\w* \w a|strong="G1437"\w* \w drink|strong="G4222"\w*; \w for|strong="G1063"\w* \w in|strong="G1909"\w* \w doing|strong="G4160"\w* \w this|strong="G3778"\w* \w you|strong="G4771"\w* \w will|strong="G3778"\w* \w heap|strong="G4987"\w* coals \w of|strong="G1909"\w* \w fire|strong="G4442"\w* \w on|strong="G1909"\w* \w his|strong="G1909"\w* \w head|strong="G2776"\w*.”\f + \fr 12:20 \ft See Proverbs 25:21-22. Presumably the ‘coals of fire’ are not literal.\f*  
\v 21 \w Do|strong="G3361"\w* \w not|strong="G3361"\w* \w be|strong="G3361"\w* \w overcome|strong="G3528"\w* \w by|strong="G1722"\w* \w evil|strong="G2556"\w*, \w but|strong="G3361"\w* \w overcome|strong="G3528"\w* \w the|strong="G1722"\w* \w evil|strong="G2556"\w* \w with|strong="G1722"\w* \w the|strong="G1722"\w* \w good|strong="G3588"\w*.\f + \fr 12:21 \ft Sounds great, but how does it work? Well, in Luke 10:19 Sovereign Jesus said: “Take note, I am giving you the authority to trample on snakes and scorpions, and over all the power of the enemy, and nothing at all may harm you.” And in Ephesians 3:20 we read: “Now to Him who is able to do immeasurably more than all we ask or imagine, according to the power that is working is us…” Please see my footnotes at those passages for an extended discussion.\f*   
\c 13  
\s1 Submit  
\m
\v 1 \w Let|strong="G1161"\w* \w every|strong="G3956"\w* \w soul|strong="G5590"\w* \w submit|strong="G5293"\w* \w to|strong="G1849"\w* \w the|strong="G3956"\w* \w governing|strong="G5242"\w* \w authorities|strong="G1849"\w*, \w because|strong="G1063"\w* \w there|strong="G1161"\w* \w is|strong="G1510"\w* \w no|strong="G3756"\w* \w authority|strong="G1849"\w* \w except|strong="G1487"\w* \w under|strong="G5259"\w* \w God|strong="G2316"\w*, \w and|strong="G1161"\w* \w the|strong="G3956"\w* existing \w authorities|strong="G1849"\w* \w have|strong="G1510"\w* \w been|strong="G1510"\w* placed \w by|strong="G5259"\w* \w God|strong="G2316"\w*.  
\v 2 \w Therefore|strong="G5620"\w* \w whoever|strong="G3588"\w* resists \w the|strong="G1161"\w* \w authority|strong="G1849"\w* \w is|strong="G3588"\w* opposed \w to|strong="G1849"\w* \w God|strong="G2316"\w*'s \w ordinance|strong="G1296"\w*, \w and|strong="G1161"\w* \w those|strong="G3588"\w* \w who|strong="G3588"\w* oppose \w will|strong="G2316"\w* \w bring|strong="G2983"\w* \w judgment|strong="G2917"\w* \w on|strong="G1161"\w* \w themselves|strong="G1438"\w*.\f + \fr 13:2 \ft God does not like anarchy.\f*  
\v 3 \w Now|strong="G1161"\w* rulers \w are|strong="G1510"\w* \w not|strong="G3756"\w* \w a|strong="G2192"\w* \w terror|strong="G5401"\w* \w to|strong="G2532"\w* \w good|strong="G3756"\w* \w deeds|strong="G2041"\w* \w but|strong="G1161"\w* \w to|strong="G2532"\w* \w bad|strong="G2556"\w* ones. \w So|strong="G2532"\w* \w if|strong="G2532"\w* \w you|strong="G1510"\w* \w wish|strong="G2309"\w* \w not|strong="G3756"\w* \w to|strong="G2532"\w* \w fear|strong="G5401"\w* \w the|strong="G2532"\w* \w authority|strong="G1849"\w*, \w do|strong="G4160"\w* \w the|strong="G2532"\w* \w good|strong="G3756"\w* \w and|strong="G2532"\w* \w you|strong="G1510"\w* \w will|strong="G2309"\w* \w have|strong="G2192"\w* \w praise|strong="G1868"\w* \w from|strong="G1537"\w* \w the|strong="G2532"\w* \w same|strong="G2532"\w*;  
\v 4 \w because|strong="G1063"\w* \w it|strong="G1161"\w* \w is|strong="G1510"\w* \w God|strong="G2316"\w*'s \w minister|strong="G1249"\w* \w to|strong="G1519"\w* \w you|strong="G4771"\w* \w with|strong="G2316"\w* \w a|strong="G1519"\w* \w view|strong="G1519"\w* \w to|strong="G1519"\w* \w the|strong="G1519"\w* \w good|strong="G3756"\w*. \w But|strong="G1161"\w* \w if|strong="G1437"\w* \w you|strong="G4771"\w* \w do|strong="G4160"\w* \w wrong|strong="G2556"\w*, \w be|strong="G1510"\w* \w afraid|strong="G5399"\w*, \w because|strong="G1063"\w* \w it|strong="G1161"\w* \w does|strong="G4160"\w* \w not|strong="G3756"\w* \w bear|strong="G4160"\w* \w the|strong="G1519"\w* \w sword|strong="G3162"\w* \w for|strong="G1063"\w* \w nothing|strong="G3756"\w*; \w because|strong="G1063"\w* \w it|strong="G1161"\w* \w is|strong="G1510"\w* \w God|strong="G2316"\w*'s \w minister|strong="G1249"\w*, \w an|strong="G1519"\w* \w avenger|strong="G1558"\w* \w with|strong="G2316"\w* \w a|strong="G1519"\w* \w view|strong="G1519"\w* \w to|strong="G1519"\w* \w wrath|strong="G3709"\w* \w on|strong="G1519"\w* \w the|strong="G1519"\w* wrongdoer.  
\v 5 \w Therefore|strong="G1352"\w* \w it|strong="G2532"\w* \w is|strong="G3588"\w* necessary \w to|strong="G2532"\w* \w submit|strong="G5293"\w*, \w not|strong="G3756"\w* \w only|strong="G3440"\w* \w because|strong="G1223"\w* \w of|strong="G1223"\w* \w the|strong="G2532"\w* \w wrath|strong="G3709"\w*, \w but|strong="G2532"\w* \w also|strong="G2532"\w* \w because|strong="G1223"\w* \w of|strong="G1223"\w* \w the|strong="G2532"\w* \w conscience|strong="G4893"\w*.\f + \fr 13:5 \ft Presumably regimes that are overtly evil are not in view. Where a regime overtly combats the good, while promoting the evil, divine guidance is especially necessary for representatives of the good, because even an evil regime exists by God's permission. That said, however, in Luke 10:19 Sovereign Jesus gives us “\+nd the\+nd* authority over all the power of the enemy”. It is therefore within the sphere of our competence to forbid any use of Satan's power in the administration of the country, in the surrounding culture, in the entertainment industry, and so on. The sky is the limit.\f*  
\v 6 \w This|strong="G3778"\w* \w is|strong="G1510"\w* precisely \w why|strong="G1223"\w* \w you|strong="G1510"\w* \w pay|strong="G5055"\w* \w taxes|strong="G5411"\w*, \w for|strong="G1063"\w* \w they|strong="G2532"\w* \w are|strong="G1510"\w* \w God|strong="G2316"\w*'s \w servants|strong="G3011"\w*, \w continually|strong="G1223"\w* attending \w on|strong="G1519"\w* \w this|strong="G3778"\w* \w very|strong="G2532"\w* \w thing|strong="G3778"\w*.\f + \fr 13:6 \ft Have you ever seen a government that didn't want more money?\f*  
\v 7 Render therefore \w to|strong="G3956"\w* \w all|strong="G3956"\w* \w their|strong="G3956"\w* \w due|strong="G3782"\w*: \w taxes|strong="G5411"\w* \w to|strong="G3956"\w* \w whom|strong="G3588"\w* \w taxes|strong="G5411"\w*, \w customs|strong="G5056"\w* \w to|strong="G3956"\w* \w whom|strong="G3588"\w* \w customs|strong="G5056"\w*, \w respect|strong="G5092"\w* \w to|strong="G3956"\w* \w whom|strong="G3588"\w* \w respect|strong="G5092"\w*, \w honor|strong="G5092"\w* \w to|strong="G3956"\w* \w whom|strong="G3588"\w* \w honor|strong="G5092"\w*.   
\s1 Love  
\p
