\v 5 \w Now|strong="G1161"\w* \w may|strong="G2532"\w* \w the|strong="G1722"\w* \w God|strong="G2316"\w* \w of|strong="G2532"\w* \w that|strong="G3588"\w* fortitude \w and|strong="G2532"\w* \w that|strong="G3588"\w* \w encouragement|strong="G3874"\w* \w grant|strong="G1325"\w* \w you|strong="G5210"\w* \w to|strong="G2532"\w* \w be|strong="G2532"\w* \w of|strong="G2532"\w* \w the|strong="G1722"\w* \w same|strong="G2532"\w* \w mind|strong="G5426"\w*\f + \fr 15:5 \ft It is only as a group of people are habitually exposed to the same Scriptures that ‘the same mind’ has much chance.\f* \w among|strong="G1722"\w* \w yourselves|strong="G4771"\w* \w according|strong="G2596"\w* \w to|strong="G2532"\w* \w Christ|strong="G5547"\w* \w Jesus|strong="G2424"\w*,  
