\s2 Glorify  
\p
\v 7 \w Therefore|strong="G1352"\w* \w accept|strong="G4355"\w* \w one|strong="G3588"\w* \w another|strong="G3588"\w*, \w just|strong="G2531"\w* \w as|strong="G2531"\w* \w the|strong="G2532"\w* \w Christ|strong="G5547"\w* \w also|strong="G2532"\w* \w accepted|strong="G4355"\w* \w us|strong="G1519"\w*,\f + \fr 15:7 \ft Perhaps 40% of the Greek manuscripts read ‘you’, but the 60% includes the best line of transmission. The verb I have rendered as ‘accept’ can also mean ‘receive’.\f* \w to|strong="G1519"\w* \w the|strong="G2532"\w* \w glory|strong="G1391"\w* \w of|strong="G2532"\w* \w God|strong="G2316"\w*.  
\v 8 \w Now|strong="G1096"\w* \w I|strong="G1063"\w* \w say|strong="G3004"\w* \w that|strong="G3588"\w* \w Christ|strong="G5547"\w* \w Jesus|strong="G3004"\w*\f + \fr 15:8 \ft “Jesus” is omitted by perhaps 4% of the Greek manuscripts, to be followed by NIV, NASB, TEV, LB, etc.—an inferior proceeding.\f* \w has|strong="G2316"\w* \w become|strong="G1096"\w* \w a|strong="G1096"\w* \w minister|strong="G1249"\w* \w to|strong="G1519"\w* \w the|strong="G1519"\w* \w circumcised|strong="G4061"\w* \w on|strong="G1519"\w* \w behalf|strong="G5228"\w* \w of|strong="G2316"\w* \w God|strong="G2316"\w*'s truth, \w in|strong="G1519"\w* order \w to|strong="G1519"\w* confirm \w the|strong="G1519"\w* \w promises|strong="G1860"\w* \w to|strong="G1519"\w* \w the|strong="G1519"\w* \w fathers|strong="G3962"\w*;  
\v 9 \w and|strong="G2532"\w* \w that|strong="G3588"\w* \w the|strong="G1722"\w* \w Gentiles|strong="G1484"\w* \w might|strong="G2532"\w* \w glorify|strong="G1392"\w* \w God|strong="G2316"\w* \w for|strong="G5228"\w* \w His|strong="G1223"\w* \w mercy|strong="G1656"\w*,\f + \fr 15:9 \ft We generally do not even trust someone who does not keep his promises, much less ‘glorify’ him. So it was necessary to fulfill the promises made to the patriarchs.\f* \w as|strong="G2531"\w* \w it|strong="G2532"\w* \w is|strong="G3588"\w* \w written|strong="G1125"\w*:  
\q1 “\w For|strong="G5228"\w* \w this|strong="G3778"\w* \w reason|strong="G1223"\w* \w I|strong="G2532"\w* \w will|strong="G2316"\w* \w give|strong="G1843"\w* \w praise|strong="G1843"\w* \w to|strong="G2532"\w* \w you|strong="G4771"\w* \w among|strong="G1722"\w* \w the|strong="G1722"\w* \w Gentiles|strong="G1484"\w*,  
